---
description: Ping NotchPill when the agent finishes a reply or needs user input.
alwaysApply: true
---

When your turn is **done**, run **one** notify (not queue + notify — that causes doubles):

```bash
./Scripts/notify-notchpill.sh "Short title" "What you finished or answered" Cursor com.todesktop.230313mzl4w4u92 "YOUR_MODEL_NAME"
```

The stop hook is a backup only if you forget. Question hooks ping automatically when you use **AskQuestion** or end with a `?`.

Always notify — including short answers. Use your real model name for the badge.
